    "created_at": "2016-08-18T02:51:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-18T02:51:13Z",
    "body": "If you don't explicitly add a \"show devtools\" menu item, there will be no explicitly way for users to open devtools after you packaged your app.\n\nHowever users can still get access to devtools by passing `--remote-debugging-port` command line switch, currently the only to prevent this is to refuse to start when such switches are detected.\n"
